classify:You|||"You tell them, 'If your fathers and sons, your brothers and wives and families and wealth, or the business you fear may fail, and the mansions that you love, are dearer to you than Allah, his Messenger, and struggling in his cause, then wait until Allah's command arrives, for Allah does not show transgressors the way.  "
